photoalbum.model

Class Album

  • java.lang.Object
    • photoalbum.model.Album
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Album>

    public class Album
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Album>
    Represents a group of photos stored under a common name. Albums are uniquely identified by a user by each having a unique name.
    Author:
    Paul Warner & Kenny Zhang
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
